name: New Holland 313 and Case IH DC133 Discbine FS22
name_original: New Holland 313 and Case IH DC133 Discbine FS22
description:
I converted my console mod the Case IH DC133 from FS19, and Diniz Farms converted the New Holland 313. We decided to combine both mods to bring you guys both brands of mowers. Unfortunately Giants software has been a pain to deal with so for now its only for PC. It's a very simple mod, however you can choose between whatever your favorite CNH brand may be.

Consider supporting my work on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/whiskeysierramodding
